high_descs: Turn around and walk to the wooden desk.
Pick up the white pen to the left of the book on the desk.
Put the pen inside the black mug near the edge of the desk.
Pick up the mug with the pen inside from the desk.
Turn around and walk to the small wooden nightstand on the left.
Put the mug with the pen on the left side of the nightstand.
anns.task_desc: Place a mug with a pen on a nightstand.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the desk.
Pick up the pen closest to the book.
Place the pen in the mug to the right of the pen still on the desk.
Turn right and walk to the night stand by the bed.
Place the mug on the night stand, behind and to the left of the keys.
anns.task_desc: Place a mug with a pen in it on a night stand.

high_descs: Turn right and take a step then turn right and walk to the desk.
Pick up the pen that's above the mug.
Put the pen in the mug that's on the desk in front of you.
Pick up the mug with the pen that's in front of you.
Take a step backwards then two steps to your right.
Put the mug on the night stand to the left of the bed.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a pen in it on the night stand.
